{
  "info": {
    "name": "API Mi Boleta",
    "description": "Colección de endpoints para la API REST de boletas, rifas y sorteos.\n\n**Versionado:** `/api/v1`\n**Autenticación:** Bearer JWT (excepto register/login).\n\nFlujo recomendado:\n1. `POST /auth/register` — crea un usuario.\n2. `POST /auth/login` — guarda el token automáticamente en la variable `token`.\n3. Usa los endpoints de tickets.\n4. Para los endpoints de admin, primero promueve el usuario en la DB: `UPDATE users SET role = 'admin' WHERE email = '...';` y vuelve a hacer login.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_postman_id": "0a73a3c1-1111-2222-3333-444444444444"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:4000/api/v1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "ticketId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Index v1",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": [""]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Juan Pérez\",\n  \"email\": \"juan@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"secret123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (json.data && json.data.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.token);",
                  "    console.log('Token guardado en variable token');",
                  "  }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"juan@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"secret123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Tras un login exitoso, el test script guarda automáticamente `data.token` en la variable `token` de la colección."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Tickets",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Crear ticket",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  if (json.data && json.data.id) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('ticketId', json.data.id);",
                  "    console.log('ticketId guardado:', json.data.id);",
                  "  }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Lotería de Medellín\",\n  \"gameType\": \"Lotería\",\n  \"gameNumber\": \"1234\",\n  \"gameDate\": \"2026-06-15T20:00:00.000Z\",\n  \"amount\": 5000,\n  \"place\": \"Tienda La Esquina\",\n  \"status\": \"Pendiente\",\n  \"notes\": \"Soñé con el número la semana pasada\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/tickets",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["tickets"]
            },
            "description": "Crea un ticket para el usuario autenticado.\n\n**gameType** debe ser uno de: Lotería, Rifa, Sorteo, Boleta, Juego ocasional.\n**status** debe ser uno de: Pendiente, Ganado, Perdido."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar tickets (con filtros)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/tickets?page=1&pageSize=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["tickets"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "pageSize", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "status", "value": "Pendiente", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "gameType", "value": "Lotería", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "q", "value": "1234", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Lista los tickets del usuario autenticado.\n\n**Query params (todos opcionales):**\n- `status`: Pendiente | Ganado | Perdido\n- `gameType`: Lotería | Rifa | Sorteo | Boleta | Juego ocasional\n- `q`: búsqueda en title y gameNumber\n- `page`: default 1\n- `pageSize`: default 20, máx 100"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Obtener ticket por ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/tickets/{{ticketId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["tickets", "{{ticketId}}"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Actualizar ticket",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"Ganado\",\n  \"notes\": \"¡Sí me lo gané!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/tickets/{{ticketId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["tickets", "{{ticketId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Actualización parcial. Todos los campos son opcionales."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Eliminar ticket",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/tickets/{{ticketId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["tickets", "{{ticketId}}"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Admin",
      "description": "Endpoints restringidos a usuarios con role = 'admin'. Promueve un usuario manualmente en la DB:\n\n`UPDATE users SET role = 'admin' WHERE email = '...';`\n\nLuego vuelve a hacer login para obtener un JWT con role embebido.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar TODOS los tickets",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/tickets?page=1&pageSize=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["admin", "tickets"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "pageSize", "value": "20" },
                { "key": "status", "value": "Pendiente", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "gameType", "value": "Lotería", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "q", "value": "juan", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "userId", "value": "<uuid>", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Lista todos los tickets de todos los usuarios. Incluye `owner` con `{id, name, email}`.\n\n**Filtros opcionales (query params):**\n- `status`, `gameType`, `q` (busca en title, gameNumber, owner.name, owner.email)\n- `userId`: filtra por dueño\n- `page`, `pageSize`\n\nRequiere JWT con role = admin (devuelve 403 si no)."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
